Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:41.71,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,[face!] 繰り返す 疎外 虚勢 絶望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:49.17,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,鎮まらぬ魂　人はなぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:58.83,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive 誰かの歯車が　so, still alive 狂い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:07.25,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,忌まわしい鐘楼が鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:17.36,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive? ‘来るべき世界’は so, still alive? 求めている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:23.28,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,処刑台の終わりなき犠牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:12.98,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,never die 歴史の血の河を　i never die かいくぐり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:20.31,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,彷徨える　我が十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:31.94,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive 命の歯車が　so, still alive 回り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:39.93,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,振り切る己をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:50.79,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive? ロゴスの誘いは　so, still alive? まだ見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:59.03,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,汚れてく異教徒たちの涙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:10.33,IN_JP_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,月の下　顔のないマリア
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.59,0:18:25.76,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,你曾拿來羞辱我的旋律 至今仍在咆哮嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.46,0:18:37.26,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,戰慄的聖堂 反抗之心
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.10,0:18:47.81,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,難以捉摸的命運女神 燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.81,0:18:56.70,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive 生命的齒輪 so, still alive 開始轉動
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.70,0:19:04.65,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,擺脫束縛 貫徹自我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.12,0:19:15.51,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive? 理性的召喚 so, still alive? 仍不可見
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.51,0:19:21.10,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,異教徒們的淚水逐漸汙濁
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.23,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,[face!] so, we gotta face this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.45,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,[face!] we gotta face
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.45,0:19:41.71,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,[face!] 重蹈覆轍 疏離 虛張聲勢 絕望
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.71,0:19:49.17,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,靈魂無法平息 人為何總如此
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.69,0:19:58.83,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive 不知何人的齒輪 so, still alive 開始錯亂
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.83,0:20:07.25,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,不祥的鐘樓鳴響
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.39,0:20:17.36,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive? 我正在追尋 so, still alive? 「應當到來的世界」
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.36,0:20:23.28,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,斷頭台上無盡的犧牲者
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.55,0:21:12.98,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,never die 奮力潛入 i never die 歷史的血河
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.45,0:21:20.31,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,我的十字架彷徨其中
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.09,0:21:31.94,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive 生命的齒輪 so, still alive 開始轉動
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.94,0:21:39.93,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,擺脫束縛 貫徹自我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.78,0:21:50.79,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,still alive? 理性的召喚 so, still alive? 仍不可見
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.79,0:21:59.03,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,異教徒們的淚水逐漸汙濁
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.21,0:22:10.33,IN_CH_EP10_M2,,0,0,0,,月光之下 無面的瑪利亞
